{"tid":2122266,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧斥習近平是「誠信破產的獨裁主義真正信奉者」","createTime":"2020-07-24T02:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T03:23:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e68910252ca560cfd4486c54a58c593e2f16bd99","tid":2122266,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:00:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539568-20200724.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539568-20200724.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6Fuzyl20%2B4TZ9N3SWLiWM4Y%3D&h=b60e4f5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539568-20200724.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cebe5d6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539568-20200724.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧就美中關係發表演講，他表示，曾經期望中國與國際社會更加合作及遵守諾言，但中共未有兌現承諾，威脅著美國的經濟、自由及全球未來的自由民主，形容與中國盲目交往的舊方式是失敗。<br />\n<br />\n他批評中共盜取知識產權、隱瞞新型肺炎的疫情，導致全球大流行，他又形容中國國家主席習近平是一名「已經誠信破產的獨裁主義思想真正信奉者」。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧在發言中，亦有提及香港，他表示，每天有關於對香港及新疆施加更多限制的新聞；<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">在北約成員國之中，有一個國家未有聲援香港</span></span></strong>，是因為懼怕北京限制進入中國市場。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧呼籲更多盟友、自由國家，以及中國民眾，與美國合作，以更創新及堅定的方式改變中國的行為。"},{"pid":"c836e9b86f5ddfe1d3443e4ce637cd2c2acd1bf0","tid":2122266,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8809555d16bf46548ca3a080aed82e2b075061","tid":2122266,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:02:33.000Z","msg":"牙奧，希望4年後，見到你坐橢圓形台辦公室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree